    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Hello,</p>

<p>is it possible to add the validation messages of the captcha to the validators?
It looks like this at the moment:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
'validators'  =&gt; array(
    array('NotEmpty', true, array(
        'messages' =&gt; array(
            Zend_Validate_NotEmpty::IS_EMPTY =&gt; 'not_empty_is_empty',
        )
    )),
)

/* Somewhere else at the captcha form element (Zend_Form_Element_Captcha) */
'imgUrl'          =&gt; 'captchas',
'messages'        =&gt; array(
    Zend_Captcha_Word::BAD_CAPTCHA    =&gt; 'captcha_bad_captcha',
    Zend_Captcha_Word::MISSING_VALUE  =&gt; 'captcha_missing_value',
    Zend_Captcha_Word::MISSING_ID     =&gt; 'captcha_missing_id'
)
</code></pre>

<p>but I want to have it like that:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
'validators'  =&gt; array(
    array('NotEmpty', true, array(
        'messages' =&gt; array(
            Zend_Validate_NotEmpty::IS_EMPTY =&gt; 'not_empty_is_empty',
        )
    )),
    array('Captcha', true, array(
        'messages' =&gt; array(
            Zend_Captcha_Word::BAD_CAPTCHA    =&gt; 'captcha_bad_captcha',
            Zend_Captcha_Word::MISSING_VALUE  =&gt; 'captcha_missing_value',
            Zend_Captcha_Word::MISSING_ID     =&gt; 'captcha_missing_id'
        )
    )),
)
</code></pre>

